column5: Looking for a high successful moose hunt in NW Ontario for 4 guys. Looking for fall 2020. Thanks for any and all help. Not rich, but probably once in a lifetime hunt. Retired older cops, not fat, but not like 30 years ago either.
Check out www.clarksresorts.com.give them a call and talk to Wayne.they have tags for area 16A.very good area and they have cabins in that area.ill be headed to Wright lake Sept 16 with 2 hunters.
